estion","name":"How is the Provider App more secure than texting patients directly?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Unlike SMS, WhatsApp, or personal calls, the Provider App uses encrypted, HIPAA-appropriate messaging that keeps PHI safe, protects your personal phone number, and creates an auditable record of patient communications."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can providers get compensated for out-of-clinic communication using the app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, where regulations and payer policies allow, the Provider App makes it easier to document, track, and bill for out-of-clinic communications such as asynchronous e-visits. The app time-stamps and records these interactions in the patient's health record."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does the app replace my desktop or web EHR?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. The Provider App is designed as a mobile companion to the Virtual Practice web platform. It brings key clinical features to your phone but does not replace the full web dashboard for administrative and configuration tasks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the Provider App free or do I need to pay extra?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Every Virtual Practice account includes the free Virtual Practice Provider App (iOS and Android). For organizations that want their own branded version, a white-labelled Provider App is available as a paid add-on."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What kinds of providers use the app?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The app is designed for solo practitioners, small clinics, and healthcare startups alike. It scales from individual use cases to team-based practices that need secure mobile access to consultations and records."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I get started with the Provider Mobile App?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Sign up for the Virtual Practice 14-day free trial. You'll get access to the web dashboard, the patient portal, and the Provider App so you can test mobile consultations, AI Scribe, and secure messaging firsthand."}}]}</script><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="text-center mb-12"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-vibrant mx-auto"></div></div><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8"><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What is the Provider Mobile App in the Virtual Practice?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What is the Provider Mobile App in the Virtual Practice?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Does the Provider App include full practice administration?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">Does the Provider App include full practice administration?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="Can I use AI Scribe from the mobile app?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">Can I use AI Scribe from the mobile app?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button></div><div class="border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0"><button aria-label="What types of consultations can providers manage in the app?" class="w-full text-left py-4 flex justify-between items-center hover:text-blue-vibrant transition-colors"><span class="font-medium">What types of consultations can providers manage in the app?</span><span class="transform transition-transform ">▼</span></button><